Package: spotr
Title: Estimate Spatial Population Indices from Ecological Abundance Data
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonas", "Knape", , "jonas.knape@slu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8012-5131"))
Description: Compute relative or absolute population trends across space using predictions from models fitted to ecological population abundance data.
             The package supports models fitted by 'mgcv' and 'brms', and draws from posterior predictive distributions.
